00165 inline void NT_cerr(NTsize currentTalkLevel, NTsize talkLevel, string message)
00166 {
00167     if (currentTalkLevel >= talkLevel) cerr << message << endl;
00168 }

00184 template<class T> inline T NT_Max(T a, T b) { return a > b ? a : b; }
00185 template<class T> inline T NT_Min(T a, T b) { return a < b ? a : b; }
